{"tid":1039972,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港電台開支預算較上個財政年度少約2千萬元","createTime":"2019-02-27T19:12:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-01T13:24:37.000Z","uid":26418,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"eb1b692ccee1d6c60099e0f9f7b07162d247f11d","tid":1039972,"uid":26418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T19:12:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>預算案撥資源60億元優化海濱及6億元翻新公廁</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n預算案延續過往勾劃，香港智慧城市藍圖，正籌備為所有本港居民，提供數碼個人身分，提升政府雲端服務。<br />\n<br />\n預算案亦增撥資源改善公共施，包括預留60億元優化海濱，設立兩億元「城市林務發展基金」保育樹木，撥款6億元分階段翻新240所公厠。<br />\n<br />\n政府會向「香港運動員基金」，注資2.5億元，支援運動員兼顧訓練和學業雙軌發展。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">至於在四月開始，提供24小時電視廣播的香港電台，開支預算較上個財政年度少約2千萬元。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1445172-20190227.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1445172-20190227.htm&d=7eOXcRQmrlFTo7mkgo38hMtxnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=0617b408\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1445172-20190227.htm&h=d0c3abd3\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1445172-20190227.htm</a>"},{"pid":"0531844bd3b14d5508f6cb7c66f3ef983c52bab1","tid":1039972,"uid":26418,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T19:14:19.000Z","msg":"繼續陰乾香港電台<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n新大樓又唔批<br />\n做24小時電視廣播 但又減開支預算"},{"pid":"e85612d05bf0a572d2d49a4e8e188dc87bff7d0a","tid":1039972,"uid":47674,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T21:20:20.000Z","msg":"下任廣播處長畀李保安做<br />\nbudget應該可以降到去0"},{"pid":"061abc7ee30819139446bf8525917f9397a3ea9a","tid":1039972,"uid":26418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0531844bd3b14d5508f6cb7c66f3ef983c52bab1","tid":1039972,"uid":26418,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T19:14:19.000Z"